---
<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-500 via-slate-300 to-slate-200 p-8 md:px-20 md:py-20 mt-5 mx-auto max-w-5xl rounded-lg flex flex-col items-center text-center">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl tracking-tight">
      <span class="gradient-text font-bold">
